description: This file provides a no-operation implementation for service worker registration and unregistration, mainly to satisfy Create React App (CRA) requirements and suppress console noise in development. It is intended for use in development and ignored in production unless explicitly imported.

methods.name: register()
methods.description: A no-op function for service worker registration, used to satisfy CRA requirements.

methods.name: unregister()
methods.description: A no-op function for unregistering service workers, included for completeness.
